page.title: 13Myself-a girl called Louise.
page.content: My name is Louise and I was born in Newcastle General Hospital in 1975. I live on Chapel House estate and go to Milecastle First School. My favourite subject is History. I do not like Maths. I have blonde hair and blue eyes and I weigh 4 stone. I have a brother called Gianni. My Dad is called Anthony George and my Mam is called Lesley Ann. I have a pet rabbit called Flopsy. My favourite food is tortilinni and belly pork. My favourite clothes are flowery skirts and dresses. My favourite pop group is Wham. My Mam and Dad drive a car, and I like riding my two-wheeled bike.
